{"tid":681668,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦食硬皇馬三大理由","createTime":"2018-05-28T08:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T08:36:40.000Z","uid":23734,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46a45254486094e8ac76945ed7f31b008b1d02f2","tid":681668,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180526&amp;sec_id=25391&amp;s=0&amp;a=20402000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180526%26sec_id%3D25391%26s%3D0%26a%3D20402000&d=bFYDW4yt9lkxTqnDWxBjIleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=7f478726\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180526%26sec_id%3D25391%26s%3D0%26a%3D20402000&h=36abca18\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180526&amp;sec_id=25391&amp;s=0&amp;a=20402000</a><br />\n<br />\n寧可信其有，世界上存在不少傳說奇聞，而「摸盃失冠」就是其中之一。凡決賽前有球員出場時多手摸盃的話，該隊就會失落冠軍。今年的歐霸盃決賽有馬賽隊長皮耶出場時「衰多手」，結果球隊就以0:3大敗予馬德里體育會，而皮耶本人更在比賽途中傷出，認真邪門！<br />\n在05年的歐聯決賽亦上演同樣「悲劇」，當年AC米蘭中場悍將加度素賽前摸了大耳朵盃，結果球隊半場領先三球下，被利物浦追平，紅軍再憑互射12碼勝出。報道指，紅軍前鋒摩連迪斯曾在更衣室警告隊友不要觸碰大耳盃，紅軍眾將亦乖乖聽話，「成就」了伊斯坦堡奇蹟。<br />\n至於今次亦是利物浦與皇家馬德里第二次在歐聯（前身歐冠盃）決賽碰頭，紅軍於80/81球季的歐冠盃決賽以1:0擊敗皇馬。無獨有偶，今年和1981年英國皇室都有大婚、德甲法蘭克福近兩次奪得德國盃亦是在1981和2018年，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>種種迹象都似季對紅軍有利</strong></span></span>，但贏波總不能只靠彩數，與其迷信於巧合，不如做好自己！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55c08acee9b9033e342c9db2aec3ac7ac16f23d","tid":681668,"uid":283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:02:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZQtEnsbM3NE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZQtEnsbM3NE&d=bFYDW4yt9lkxTqnDWxBjIleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=b6132e7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZQtEnsbM3NE</a><br />\n